{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回：友情。纤纤在金川的利诱下挣扎，试图以婚姻条件稳住金川，但金川自称孤儿令她心寒。小侯爷赵某及时出现救下纤纤，金川被赶走后怨毒满怀。小雷在荒野墓碑前痛哭失声，雪衣女（丁残艳）出现，以讥讽刺痛小雷，揭示纤纤已与金川在一起。丁残艳自报名字，小雷冷漠离去。龙四镖局在茶亭歇息，小雷前来还情，与龙四对饮。枯瘦老人送来一幅暗藏杀机的画，镖局气氛骤变。小雷以骡子脾气自比，表达对友情的执着，与龙四握手言和。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "我怎么会想赶你走，可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "可是怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "我……我觉得，像这样的大事，总不应该就这样匆匆忙忙的决定了，总应该先回去，告诉你的父母一声。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "我知道你也许会觉得我太多事，但是，我是孤苦伶仃的女孩子，既没有朋友，也没有亲人，你以后……你以后若是欺负了我，我也可以有个保障。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "我的身世，好像始终都没有告诉过你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "你没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "我也跟你一样，是个无父无母的孤儿，甚至连朋友都没有几个。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "就因为我们都是孤苦伶仃的人，所以更应该互相依靠，你说是不是？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小侯爷",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "她说的话你听见了没有？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我走。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫他出去，马上出去。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "你说我不该这样子对你的，但你可知道我为什么会这样对你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "因为你，是你自己想要叫我这么样做的。一开始本是你在诱惑我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "你以为我什么都不知道？你以为我是个呆子？你以为我真的已被你迷住？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "我本来是不愿再想他的，可是我只要一见着你，就会想到他，因为你们本就是好朋友，你本不该这样子对我的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "你答应过我，永远不再提起他。永远不再想他的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "你是不是时常在想，希望我跟小雷越快翻脸越好，好让你有机会得到我。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "你知不知道，自从我第一眼看上你的时候，就已经喜欢你了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "像我们这种人，天生就应该厮守在一起的，我若不对你好，还有谁会对你好？你难道还有什么顾虑？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_jin_chuan",
      "text": "我本是不愿再想他的，可是我只要一见着你，就会想到他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "金川",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "这本是你自己要的，你怨不得我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放开我，让我走……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你哭够了么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "若是哭够，就该站起来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我想不到畜生也会哭。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "text": "畜生会哭，母狗也会哭。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "母狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "text": "我是畜生，你是母狗。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你认得的女人若全是母狗，你也许就不会哭得如此伤心了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "母狗至少比较忠实，至少不会跟着别人走。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你砍断了我一只手，又侮辱了我，现在不妨再把我扼死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我让你砍断我的手，让你侮辱我，情愿被你扼死，你可知道为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我这么样做，只因为我可怜你，只因为你已不值得我动手杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你已不值得任何人动手杀你，因为你自己已经毁了自己，别人在床上大笑的时候，你却只能野狗般躲在这里干嚎。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "text": "别人？你说的是谁？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你应该知道是谁。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "text": "你看见了他们？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "现在我只看得见你一双脏手。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "雪衣女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我是看见了他们，也看见了她。她就算是条母狗，也是条饿极了的母狗。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "丁残艳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你就算不愿再碰我，不愿跟我再说一句话，至少也该问问我的名字。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "丁残艳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我是你的情人也好，是你的仇人也好，你也至少应该问问我的名字。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "丁残艳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "难道我在你心中，竟是个这么样不足轻重的人？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "丁残艳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "难道你真的已将我们之间的恩怨情仇，全都忘记？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_yi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "丁残艳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也是个人，我也有名字，我的名字叫丁残艳……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "兄弟，雷兄弟，龙四在这里。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "我不是你的兄弟。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我知道，我们不是朋友，也不是兄弟，可是你进来喝碗酒行不行？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "我本就是来找你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "找我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "我从不愿欠人的情。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你没有欠我的情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "有！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "只不过雷家死的人，也用不着你姓龙的去埋葬。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我早就知道那老头子难免多嘴的，这世上能守密的人好像是已越来越少了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳急",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "这也并不是什么见不得人的事，若有人埋葬了我家的人，我感激还来不及。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ji",
      "text": "下次无论你家死了多少人，我都会替你埋葬。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我不是你，我一向没这种习惯。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳急",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你想怎么样？难道一定要我们也死几个人让你埋葬，这笔账才能扯平？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "我欠你的情，我若有八百两银子，一定还你，我没有，所以我来找你。无论你要我做什么，只要开口就行。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你欠我的情也好，不欠也好，只要能陪我喝几杯酒，龙四已心满意足了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒来！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让他走，先看看这包袱里是什么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他想必是路上中了暑，抬他下去歇歇，就会好的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "雷公子真是江海之量，无人能及，只可惜在下等已无法奉陪了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "雷公子请便。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "请便是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "雷公子与在下等本不是走一条路的，此刻既已尽欢。正好分手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "好，好朋友，龙刚龙四爷果然是个好朋友。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我们不是朋友。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "不是！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "我们是朋友也好，不是也好，反正我跟你走的是一条路。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你为何一定要跟着我走？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "因为我这人本就是天生的骡子脾气。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ji",
      "text": "你说是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳急",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ji",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "做骡子并没有什么好处。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "至少有一点好处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si",
      "speaker_name": "龙四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_long_si",
      "text": "骡子至少不会出卖朋友，朋友有了危难时，他也不会走，你就算用鞭子去抽他，他说不走，就是不走。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 702
    }
